      "description": "Hello,\nthis is Heedam :)\n\nI capture every moment of everyday life in photos.\n\nOrdinary moments from daily life,\nbeautiful moments gifted by the four seasons,\nprecious moments with friends, loved ones, and family,\nand special moments from my travels.\n\nTo help you capture joyful moments\nmore clearly, beautifully,\nand in a more special way,\nI prepared 52 different filters.\n\nHeedam offers filters optimized for people who love landscapes, nature,\nand bright, rich colors.\nMake your photos and videos feel even more special with a variety of filters.\n\n——————\n\nFilter List\n\n1. Daily: Natural colors that never feel too much\n(daily1, daily2, cafe1, cafe2, food1, food2, food3, sunset1, sunset2, sunset3, night1, night2)\n\n2. Season: Colors that bring out the mood of each season\n(spring1, spring2, spring3, spring4, spring5, summer1, summer2, summer3, summer4, fall1, fall2, fall3, winter1, winter2, winter3, christmas1, christmas2)\n\n3. Film: Bright film-like tones + grain\n(film1, film2, film3, film4, film5, film6, film7)\n\n4. Mood: Rich saturation + mist\n(dream1, dream2, skyfilm, travel1, travel2, ocean, seoul, mood1, mood2, mood3, mood4,\ntwilight1, twilight2, twilight3, cinematic1, cinematic2)\n\n#Optimized more for landscapes and aesthetic photos than selfies.\n\n#All features included with no extra payment\nYou can use all filters without any additional in-app purchases.\nNo monthly subscription. Use it continuously with a one-time purchase.\n\nSimple, fast, and convenient features.\n- Take photos right after applying a filter.\n- Video recording has been added!\n- Add grain with one tap.\n- Add mist with one tap.\n- Adjust filter intensity.\n- Apply filters to captured images.\n- RAW file support for DSLR and mirrorless cameras has been added. (1.3.0)\n- High-resolution images over 20MB can also be edited. (1.3.0)\n- Apply filters to captured videos.\n\n◇ Instagram\nCheck out new photos and updates at @heedam_i.\n\n◇ Contact\nIf you have any issues using the app or need anything,\nplease contact us at heedami02@gmail.com or Instagram @heedam_i.\n\nHee means joy, Dam means to capture.\nCapture joy.",
